movieio.jmf

Class JMFFramePushDataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.media.protocol.DataSource
      • javax.media.protocol.PushBufferDataSource
        • movieio.jmf.JMFFramePushDataSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.media.Controls, javax.media.Duration

    public class JMFFramePushDataSource
extends javax.media.protocol.PushBufferDataSource
    A DataSource to sequentially read images and turn them into a stream of JMF buffers. The DataSource is not seekable or positionable.
